<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1395256-if-one-loves-this-book-play-what-else">If one loves this book/play, what else would one love? Recommendations, please.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1395256'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F72003.Angels_in_America">like</a></span>

</li>
