<span id="freeTextContainer14077163466995595580">“Unspeakable beauty. That’s something I would like to see.”<br/><br/>I think it&apos;s easy to see why this play had such a huge impact when it came out. It&apos;s written so beautifully and impactfully and the characters stay with you a long time. It&apos;s quickly become one of my favorite literary works ever.</span>
  <span id="freeText14077163466995595580" style="display:none">“Unspeakable beauty. That’s something I would like to see.”<br /><br />I think it's easy to see why this play had such a huge impact when it came out. It's written so beautifully and impactfully and the characters stay with you a long time. It's quickly become one of my favorite literary works ever.</span>
