      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/35822.Tony_Kushner">About Tony Kushner</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/35822.Tony_Kushner"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1209471902p3/35822.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/35822.Tony_Kushner">Tony Kushner
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
370
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer15661247253972439483">Tony Kushner is an award-winning American playwright most famous for his play <i>Angels in America</i>, for which he was awarded the Pulitzer Prize. He is also co-author, along with Eric Roth, of the screenplay of the 2005 film <i>Munich</i>, which was directed by Steven Spielberg and earned Kushner (along with Roth) an Academy Award nomination for Best Adapted Screenplay.</span>

</div>
</div>

